data.description: This home is a "Must See!! "Updated 3-Bedroom, 2-bathroom, 2-car garage, Fully Fenced Home in Highly Desired Golden Gate Estates SW.  This newly renovated home comes complete with Impact Glass/Sliders, new luxury core vinyl flooring, paint, baseboards, trim, fixtures, appliances, etc.. New Reverse Osmosis System!!!! Plenty of space for RV, boats and for business owners to Park equipment with 1.14 acres of land!! This well maintained home will not last. Home comes with Zosi surveillance system, Samsung TV,  Full security surveillance, New roof comes with 15 year transferable warranty and wind mitigation. All sheds boats And belongings on property will be removed upon purchase. Don't miss the chance to make this remarkable home yours!
